>Available from: <uri xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="http://www.who.int/nutrition/publications/micronutrients/guidelines_for_Iron_supplementation.pdf">http://www.who.int/nutrition/publications/micronutrients/guidelines_for_Iron_supplementation.pdf</uri></comment></element-citation></ref></ref-list></back></article>